result.name: King Cafe

reviews.text: The scrambled eggs on rice with bbq porks and shrimps is a signature dish. Price is above average amongst other restaurants but the final product is really good. The scrambled egg is creamy and juicy, the bbq porks are individually pan fried to make them more tasty. There is also a "secret" sweet soy sauce on the rice. The green onions and shrimps are also perfect addition to the dish.
Comfortable place, nice and delicious food
The tomato soup noodle is delicious and the soup itself is very tasty! Seats are a bit crowded and the hotdog is huge !!
Full! Big in size , classic HK style dish and Milk tea
Fairly priced HK-style restaurant

reviews.text: 各種餐食價錢頗貴，最唔好係水都無一杯给客人，變相迫人付錢配杯飲品！
Ok、地方幹淨，坐下都舒服
環境舒適，食物可以接受！

可能別人愛吃，
但不是我杯茶。
一般街坊餐廳,食物質數唔差,有空可以試吓無妨。
